TYPE ERROR :
Errors that might be returned by functionblocks from this library typically
using the variable eError.

FILE_TRANSFER_SERVICES_NOT_SUPPORTED

BLOCKED_DUE_TO_ONLINECHANGE

change is in progress
CANCELLED_DUE_TO_ONLINE_CHANGE
The operation was cancelled because an online change was
executed between start and end of the operation
